Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.73,0:00:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况危险度增加225%
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建议先行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.87,0:00:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你能翻译的词汇告诉他们我方不是敌人
